WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.783
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.783 --> 00:00:03.310
How are y'all doing?

00:00:03.310 --> 00:00:06.243
Well, glory to God, it was an amazing week.

00:00:06.625 --> 00:00:10.812
I just want to show you my shirt again.

00:00:10.812 --> 00:00:15.840
I know if you haven't been on my broadcast here and seen this, it says 'Jesus the Healer.

00:00:15.840 --> 00:00:20.640
' I got this at Nancy Dufresne's where they were having a healing service, and I still love this.

00:00:20.640 --> 00:00:22.218
I'm going to keep it out there all the time.

00:00:22.218 --> 00:00:24.582
You can get it on her website.

00:00:25.275 --> 00:00:30.099
This is Diana; she got this on Amazon and I thought this was cute.

00:00:30.099 --> 00:00:31.820
She says, 'Make Heaven crowded.

00:00:31.820 --> 00:00:33.120
' Yep, make Heaven crowded.

00:00:33.120 --> 00:00:34.320
I thought it was fun.

00:00:34.320 --> 00:00:35.460
I just like witty stuff.

00:00:41.893 --> 00:00:46.900
One of the prophetic words of the Lord told me about the glory.

00:00:46.900 --> 00:00:52.360
He said that the glory would show up at Sister Billye Brim's prayer conference.

00:00:52.360 --> 00:01:00.669
Well, we went through the whole week and I was about ready to go home because I didn't see what the Lord showed me in the vision.

00:01:00.984 --> 00:01:05.855
I was really bummed about it because I knew what the Lord showed me when I was praying.

00:01:06.100 --> 00:01:11.937
So I said, 'Lord, I know I didn't miss it,' because I know you showed it to me.

00:01:12.119 --> 00:01:18.249
When I see a vision and I'm hearing from the Lord, I know I've heard the Lord; I don't question it, it's that clear.

00:01:18.977 --> 00:01:49.493
I was packing my stuff to come home on Sunday, and I told my wife, 'I'm going home, I'm tired.

00:01:49.493 --> 00:02:11.240
' But the Lord said, 'Brandon, if you go home, you're missing it.

00:02:14.130 --> 00:02:26.150
You have to go to the tent meeting.

00:02:26.150 --> 00:02:45.544
' We were checking out and He said, 'Check back in.

00:02:45.544 --> 00:02:48.800
Check back in.

00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:59.729
' So I was like, 'Well, okay.

00:02:59.729 --> 00:03:23.640
' I told Diana that something was going to happen supernaturally at the tent meeting.

00:03:23.640 --> 00:03:30.599
We were anticipating it.

00:03:33.929 --> 00:03:52.580
I told Sister Billye, 'The Lord said that something's going to happen at the tent meeting.

00:03:52.580 --> 00:03:58.409
' This is awesome.

00:03:58.409 --> 00:04:20.031
We go to the tent revival because I told you it's going to start with Billye.

00:04:36.320 --> 00:04:37.897
I saw the glory come in a cloud at Billye Brim's service.

00:04:37.897 --> 00:05:15.520
The Lord told me that starting from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah, it would be first the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation of what was coming.

00:05:15.520 --> 00:05:27.931
We would start to see the outpouring of healings manifest.

00:05:27.931 --> 00:05:42.017
But He said it would start at Billye's prayer conference.

00:05:57.360 --> 00:06:28.870
I was excited about it because I know in my spirit that we are there and it's time to start to see the demonstrations and manifestations of the glory of God.

00:06:29.410 --> 00:06:44.400
Like I said, we went all week and didn't see anything.

00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:58.990
So we were leaving, and I was just disappointed.

00:07:01.340 --> 00:07:06.840
The Lord said, 'Don't.

00:07:06.840 --> 00:07:19.545
' So we went to the tent meeting.

00:07:19.545 --> 00:07:44.582
The offerings were taken, the preaching was completely done, and they were getting ready to dismiss the church.

00:07:46.039 --> 00:07:56.210
I am staring up in the sky going, 'What gives, Lord?

00:07:56.210 --> 00:07:59.324
What happened?

00:07:59.324 --> 00:08:03.381
There's crickets, nothing.

00:08:03.381 --> 00:08:19.461
' All of a sudden, Diana sees the glory cloud come in.

00:08:27.116 --> 00:08:40.260
I had a glimpse of it before during the service, and I was thinking, 'Is that You, Lord?

00:08:40.260 --> 00:08:45.807
' in a vision.

00:08:46.868 --> 00:09:00.292
I see the same thing she's seeing in the spirit.

00:09:06.287 --> 00:09:13.803
It came up halfway to one of the tent poles right by the stage, but it wasn't on the stage, it was right beside it.

00:09:17.095 --> 00:09:19.013
It just hovered there.

00:09:19.564 --> 00:09:24.825
It stayed right there.

00:09:27.570 --> 00:09:47.855
It wasn't around the speaker on the stage; it was just like a pillar.

00:09:47.855 --> 00:09:49.315
How big do you think it was?

00:09:57.404 --> 00:10:02.470
It was probably about three or four feet tall.

00:10:02.470 --> 00:10:22.697
It was the size of a small child, but it was definitely there.

00:10:22.697 --> 00:10:47.399
It was like a heavy mist, a cloud-looking thing around that tent pole right there.

00:10:50.040 --> 00:10:55.840
I compared it to all the other tent poles, and none of them had that.

00:10:58.640 --> 00:11:15.965
I even rubbed my eyes again and I looked and I said, 'That's the glory.

00:11:15.965 --> 00:11:37.399
' I kept blinking and thinking, 'Do I have a film on my eye?

00:11:37.399 --> 00:11:59.100
Is it like when you get those eye boogers or whatever and you're rubbing your eye?

00:11:59.100 --> 00:12:20.698
' I tell you, the man that I was shown in the throne room flies into the meeting.

00:12:22.950 --> 00:12:32.310
I see him and I'm like, 'Oh my gosh!

00:12:32.310 --> 00:13:13.899
' because whenever I went to the throne room and the Lord said, 'I am that I am,' there was a man praying at the throne for the nations.

00:13:13.899 --> 00:13:41.975
His prayers were going before the Father, circling the throne room like a comet or a fireball.

00:13:41.975 --> 00:14:12.209
They went inside of the Lord, and He was breathing in the prayers and they were coming out of His mouth, going all throughout the throne.

00:14:12.209 --> 00:14:31.715
This man was interceding for the glorious outpouring in the nations.

00:14:31.715 --> 00:14:46.480
This is the man that the Lord showed me.

00:14:46.480 --> 00:15:36.445
He shows up at the tent revival, and I spoke to him and said, 'Wow, I've waited for so long to talk to you because of what the Lord showed me.

00:15:36.445 --> 00:16:19.982
' He was excited to meet me and we talked, but I didn't know that the Lord spoke to him about the tent meeting too, and that's why he flew there.

00:16:19.982 --> 00:16:32.875
Next, the guest speaker completely leaves with his family.

00:16:32.875 --> 00:16:36.297
They're gone.

00:16:36.297 --> 00:16:50.404
Sister Billye is getting ready to dismiss the crowd.

00:16:50.404 --> 00:17:16.079
This man comes up and says, 'I have a word to give about healings.

00:17:16.079 --> 00:17:29.615
' The Lord said He's not done with the service yet.

00:17:29.615 --> 00:18:16.463
He was shown on the way here in the plane that there were going to be creative miracles, signs, and wonders in this tent meeting, just like the Lord showed me.

00:18:16.463 --> 00:18:36.673
As he said that, I saw that the glory cloud started spreading.

00:18:53.424 --> 00:18:54.220
You could just feel the tangible presence of the Lord.

00:18:54.220 --> 00:19:16.445
As it spread, you could see it above the people's heads.

00:19:16.445 --> 00:19:28.010
You could see that thick mist.

00:19:28.010 --> 00:20:13.754
It was almost like whenever you get out of a really, really hot shower; it was like a thick fog like that, but it was like oxygen that you were breathing.

00:20:18.179 --> 00:20:31.472
It was thicker at the top and it was thinner at the bottom.

00:20:31.472 --> 00:20:54.575
It was just a heavy mist, like a fog across the top of everybody's heads.

00:21:04.395 --> 00:21:04.586
I said, 'The glory's here!

00:21:04.586 --> 00:21:15.300
' and I just started screaming, 'The glory is here!

00:21:15.300 --> 00:21:42.107
' I am worshiping the Lord, holding one of the metal tent poles, and Diana took her hand and hit me.

00:21:42.640 --> 00:21:53.800
The power of God knocked me on my nees.

00:21:53.800 --> 00:22:32.473
I fell back, boom, and I hit the chair because the power of God was all over her and the glory came all over me.

00:22:32.473 --> 00:22:48.697
Then our little girl fell out in the Holy Spirit.

00:22:48.697 --> 00:23:13.480
When Diana said the glory is here, my little girl went 'boop' and hit the ground.

00:23:13.480 --> 00:23:35.833
I fell out and hit the chair and went 'wow' because it was amazing.

00:23:35.833 --> 00:23:50.191
Then he ran out through the crowd laying hands on people.

00:23:50.191 --> 00:24:18.999
As he did that, the glory cloud just rose until it reached all the way to the top peaks of the tent.

00:24:18.999 --> 00:24:38.635
It went all the way up and it was everywhere.

00:24:38.635 --> 00:24:58.199
Even with the tent flaps open, it stayed inside the tent, permeating everything.

00:24:58.199 --> 00:25:28.600
As I saw people, they were breathing it in and I could see them getting healed without even anybody touching them.

00:25:39.640 --> 00:25:39.850
It was amazing.

00:25:39.850 --> 00:25:50.234
It was the coolest, like Azusa Street.

00:25:50.234 --> 00:26:04.574
It was exactly like that, like a glory cloud.

00:26:04.574 --> 00:26:28.939
I just kept screaming, 'The glory is here,' so many times that I almost lost my voice.

00:26:28.939 --> 00:26:41.347
We were so excited because we've waited on this moment.

00:26:41.347 --> 00:26:56.945
Thank You, Lord, for healing Your people.

00:26:56.945 --> 00:27:25.155
Let us bring glory to Your name, that Your name would be great among all Your people.

00:27:25.155 --> 00:27:45.345
Then Pastor Tracy started calling out the names and what the Lord was healing.

00:27:45.345 --> 00:28:02.650
He said there are people getting healed of their shoulders.

00:28:02.650 --> 00:28:42.160
Diana's shoulder was hurting for a while, and the power of God hit her shoulder and it was completely healed.

00:28:47.551 --> 00:29:11.316
He was saying, 'Do what you couldn't do before,' and she was rotating that whole entire shoulder joint.

00:29:11.316 --> 00:29:30.080
By the second time she did it, the pain just dissipated.

00:29:30.080 --> 00:29:38.213
It was really intense pain.

00:29:38.213 --> 00:29:45.382
People got healed of hearts.

00:29:59.116 --> 00:30:23.919
The power of God was touching people, and the angels were coming and distributing new hearts, giving body parts, and people had new livers.

00:30:23.919 --> 00:30:29.224
Just signs and wonders.

00:30:29.224 --> 00:30:56.949
If you go back to what the Lord showed me, He said, 'Brandon, the miracles would start at Billye's.

00:30:56.949 --> 00:31:20.538
' I was thinking, 'Lord, I guess I missed it,' and then suddenly the glory showed up.

00:31:20.538 --> 00:31:32.515
This is that what the Lord said.

00:31:32.515 --> 00:31:36.497
This is that.

00:31:36.497 --> 00:31:48.614
I was just weeping, watching all the people.

00:31:48.614 --> 00:31:55.137
Everybody was being touched.

00:32:00.250 --> 00:32:18.062
I think they were all in shock because they were dismissing the church when the glory showed up.

00:32:18.062 --> 00:32:33.538
Even Sister Billye, I could see it on her face.

00:32:33.538 --> 00:32:46.167
She was kind of like, 'What is going on in here?

00:32:46.167 --> 00:33:12.988
' She walked over to the side where we were sitting, and I said, 'I told you so!

00:33:12.988 --> 00:33:37.930
I told you this is what I was trying to say.

00:33:39.875 --> 00:33:43.835
The glory is this.

00:33:43.835 --> 00:34:02.744
' It's time to believe for the impossible.

00:34:02.744 --> 00:34:54.540
Now, I'm telling you, we are in the hour that creative miracles, demonstrations, and manifestations of the glory are going to start coming on the earth like we've never seen before.

00:34:54.540 --> 00:35:02.293
It's time to get excited.

00:35:02.293 --> 00:35:14.000
It's an exciting time to be alive.

00:35:14.000 --> 00:35:23.982
We're seeing a move of God.

00:35:23.982 --> 00:36:01.884
I have never ever been to a revival like that in my entire life, and I've been to tons of revivals like Kenneth Hagin's and everything.

00:36:01.884 --> 00:36:34.600
Those were amazing too, but I've never been to one quite like this where He allowed me to see the manifestation of glory all over the people.

00:36:44.196 --> 00:36:53.240
I went up on the stage because Billye said I could.

00:36:53.240 --> 00:37:05.464
As I described how I saw the people breathing it in and getting healed, there was a man the Holy Spirit drew my focus to.

00:37:05.464 --> 00:37:33.520
He lifted his head up to the heavens and the Lord said, 'I just healed him.

00:37:33.520 --> 00:37:39.733
' I wept again.

00:37:39.733 --> 00:37:55.040
It was the most amazing thing, something so precious and holy.

00:37:58.000 --> 00:38:28.200
It's amazing when you see people who have been suffering for so long and you see the power of God setting them free.

00:38:28.200 --> 00:38:51.432
The service started at noon and didn't get over until 2:00.

00:38:59.879 --> 00:39:05.370
You lose yourself in a service like that.

00:39:05.370 --> 00:39:22.822
Diana, you lose track of time in the glory.

00:39:22.822 --> 00:40:12.013
We've talked about how it's going to start in Branson, Missouri, in the theaters with Hannah and her mama, and even what the Lord showed us at the Glorious Church.

00:40:12.013 --> 00:40:47.210
I'm telling you all, I really believe, just like He said, first the blade, then the ear, and then the full manifestation.

00:40:47.210 --> 00:40:58.084
We're living in the end times.

00:41:03.133 --> 00:41:11.240
The revival is happening; this is the beginning.

00:41:24.990 --> 00:41:25.280
It's going to be a quick work.

00:41:25.280 --> 00:41:35.755
It's time to get excited and radical.

00:41:35.755 --> 00:41:40.053
He's coming!

00:41:40.053 --> 00:42:09.127
People say, 'I've heard that before; my grandma told me that since 1907.

00:42:09.127 --> 00:42:28.028
' No, you all need to listen to me.

00:42:28.028 --> 00:42:48.960
When I hear God and tell you I see something, I see something.

00:42:48.960 --> 00:43:15.754
I'm trying to warn you about the Yankees and praying over their game in the World Series.

00:43:22.304 --> 00:43:37.743
I told you to intercede that there would be no attack against the games.

00:43:37.743 --> 00:43:44.720
We have to pray about distractions.

00:43:46.099 --> 00:44:02.070
You say the October surprise hasn't come; surprise is not a bad word.

00:44:02.070 --> 00:44:12.240
Surprise is 'the glory is here.

00:44:12.240 --> 00:44:26.374
' Surprise is 'I'm going to bring my demonstrations.

00:44:26.374 --> 00:44:34.359
' It's not a 'poo-poo package.

00:44:34.359 --> 00:44:50.333
' God is a good God and the devil's a bad devil.

00:44:50.333 --> 00:44:57.063
I've seen the bubble pop.

00:44:57.063 --> 00:45:23.337
I've seen what the devil was trying to do with the economy and the government with terrorist attacks.

00:45:23.337 --> 00:45:49.920
But if my people who are called by my name will humble themselves and pray, then I will heal their land.

00:45:49.920 --> 00:45:54.519
That's a covenant promise.

00:45:54.519 --> 00:46:21.960
He said, 'Brandon, start prayer on this channel for the next 30 plus days interceding for America.

00:46:21.960 --> 00:46:34.960
' We're praying for the elections two weeks from tomorrow.

00:46:39.226 --> 00:46:55.464
I believe we have power and authority over the devil to bind him up.

00:46:55.464 --> 00:47:16.319
We are taking authority over that Antichrist spirit and saying, 'It's not time.

00:47:16.319 --> 00:48:09.920
' We will have our revival and a harvest of souls like this world has never seen before.

00:48:17.987 --> 00:48:22.104
We will have a billion-soul harvest.

00:48:22.104 --> 00:48:37.079
We're not leaving this earth defeated.

00:48:37.079 --> 00:48:43.035
God wins.

00:48:43.035 --> 00:48:51.144
Spoiler alert: He wins.

00:49:05.573 --> 00:49:06.040
It's an exciting time to be alive.

00:49:06.040 --> 00:49:27.825
You're alive right now for such a time as this.

00:49:44.960 --> 00:49:45.240
The Lord said, 'My people are thirsty, Brandon.

00:50:08.147 --> 00:50:08.513
Bring them a drink; bring them some hope.

00:50:08.513 --> 00:50:51.650
' You've got the glory on one side, and darkness is going to get darker on the other.

00:50:56.260 --> 00:51:14.527
The birthing pains will not stop; they're going to increase.

00:51:14.527 --> 00:51:46.353
But the glory is coming to the church and it's going to outshine it all.

00:51:46.353 --> 00:52:05.665
Diana could smell the fragrance of His presence again.

00:52:05.665 --> 00:52:43.040
If you have the opportunity to get in Holy Ghost meetings, you should.

00:52:43.040 --> 00:53:06.720
There were so many who flew in from all parts of the United States.

00:53:16.428 --> 00:53:26.559
I talked to a lady from Rhode Island; her husband just got born again.

00:53:26.559 --> 00:53:53.871
She was looking for healing in her own life, and the power of God was tangible on my hand.

00:53:54.653 --> 00:55:01.429
I felt the power of God go into her mind because the Lord said, 'You pray for her, Brandon.

00:55:01.429 --> 00:55:07.960
' I laid hands on her and I'm believing God she's set free.

00:55:07.960 --> 00:55:20.120
If not us, who will?

00:55:20.120 --> 00:55:26.506
We're His body.

00:55:26.506 --> 00:55:53.977
He said lay hands on the sick and they will recover.

00:56:16.389 --> 00:56:16.817
We have got to take the land.

00:56:32.619 --> 00:56:35.451
The harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

00:56:39.199 --> 00:56:59.864
Jesus asked me, 'Will you help me bring in the harvest?

00:56:59.864 --> 00:57:28.553
' How hungry and desperate are you for this move of God?

00:57:28.553 --> 00:57:42.688
It's time to believe God for the impossible.

00:57:44.805 --> 00:58:37.377
The older generation will stay; I saw the glory restoring them like Moses, so their eyes would not grow dim and their youth would be renewed like the eagles.

00:58:45.187 --> 00:58:45.449
The Lord spoke to Diana.
